name: ObjectStyleExportTagMaps
shortdesc: A collection of object style export tag maps.

parameters.name: withProperties
parameters.shortdesc: Initial values for properties of the new ObjectStyleExportTagMap (Optional)

method.name: count
method.shortdesc: Displays the number of elements in the ObjectStyleExportTagMap.

method.name: item
method.shortdesc: Returns the ObjectStyleExportTagMap with the specified index or name.

parameters.name: index
parameters.shortdesc: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

method.name: itemByRange
method.shortdesc: Returns the ObjectStyleExportTagMaps within the specified range.

parameters.name: from
parameters.shortdesc: The ObjectStyleExportTagMap, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: ObjectStyleExportTagMap, Long Integer or String.

parameters.name: to
parameters.shortdesc: The ObjectStyleExportTagMap, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: ObjectStyleExportTagMap, Long Integer or String.

method.name: firstItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the first ObjectStyleExportTagMap in the collection.

method.name: lastItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the last ObjectStyleExportTagMap in the collection.

method.name: middleItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the middle ObjectStyleExportTagMap in the collection.

method.name: previousItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the ObjectStyleExportTagMap with the index previous to the specified index.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.shortdesc: The index of the ObjectStyleExportTagMap that follows the desired ObjectStyleExportTagMap.

method.name: nextItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the ObjectStyleExportTagMap whose index follows the specified ObjectStyleExportTagMap in the collection.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.shortdesc: The ObjectStyleExportTagMap whose index comes before the desired ObjectStyleExportTagMap.

method.name: anyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns any ObjectStyleExportTagMap in the collection.

method.name: everyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns every ObjectStyleExportTagMap in the collection.

method.name: toSource
